	<entry name="AstraMilitarum/PurgeTheXenos" value="Purge the Xenos"/>
	<entry name="AstraMilitarum/PurgeTheXenosDescription" value="Increased damage to allied units within 2 tiles of The Fortress of Arrogance, and increased attacks to adjacent allied units. These increases are further improved for members of the Steel Legion. Allies which are 2 tiles away have reduced ranged damage reduction."/>
	<entry name="AstraMilitarum/PurgeTheXenosFlavor" value="&quot;Heroes of Armageddon! You have withstood the evil savagery of the Orks, and they having nothing left for you to fear. So raise high the black banners of vengeance - now is our time.&quot; - Commissar Sebastian Yarrick, during the Third War for Armageddon"/>
